caption: Plants deserve a little love, too. That's why we created The Green Album, a collection of spoken word tracks to help plants grow, narrated by @chrisodowd!🌱For every Spotify stream we'll plant one tree (up to 25,000) through support of @onetreeplanted. It's our way of giving back to the planet and helping it flourish, one tree at a time. 🌎❤️
